%F A004006 a(n) = Sum_{i=1..n} binomial(n-2i,2). - _Wesley Ivan Hurt_, Nov 18 2017
%F A004006 a(n) = n + Sum_{k=0..n} k*(n-k). - _Gionata Neri_, May 19 2018
%F A004006 a(n) = Sum_{k=0..n-1} A000124(k). - _Torlach Rush_, Aug 05 2018
